chamber_notes: the chambers were installed the night before measurements, allowing the weight and disturbance to settle before the data were collected. The chambers were generally collecting measurements in sunlite conditions, but a few points throughout the collection period were collected under dark conditions
salinity_notes: The general salinity for the GCREW marsh has been established at the site from years of measurement.
wetland_vegetation_notes: each chamber site was selected based on what was known about that portion of the marsh
